title: Captain Cool Takes A Train Journey With His Jharkhand Teammates And We Have Got Pictures
text:
IN Sports ON 22 Feb, 2017 Captain Cool Takes A Train Journey With His Jharkhand Teammates And We Have Got Pictures Share on twitter Follow Us On 
Known for his unconventional captaincy style pulling off surprising decisions on the field, former Indian skipper Mahendra Singh Dhoni continues doing the same off the field. 
After retiring from test cricket and giving up his captaincy in ODIs, captain cool has been spending quality time with his family, friends and Jharkhand teammates. Captain Cool Takes A Train Journey With His Jharkhand Teammates And We Have Got Pictures 754 396
